IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. NumberSorting.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
   01 WS-NUMBERS.
      05 WS-NUMBER PIC 9(3) OCCURS 10 TIMES.
   01 WS-TEMP PIC 9(3).
   01 WS-I PIC 9(2).
   01 WS-J PIC 9(2).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > 10
       DISPLAY "Enter number " WS-I ": " WITH NO ADVANCING
       ACCEPT WS-NUMBER(WS-I)
    END-PERFORM.

    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I = 9
       PERFORM VARYING WS-J FROM WS-I + 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-J = 10
          IF WS-NUMBER(WS-I) > WS-NUMBER(WS-J)
             MOVE WS-NUMBER(WS-I) TO WS-TEMP
             MOVE WS-NUMBER(WS-J) TO WS-NUMBER(WS-I)
             MOVE WS-TEMP TO WS-NUMBER(WS-J)
          END-IF
       END-PERFORM
    END-PERFORM.

    DISPLAY "Sorted numbers: ".
    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > 10
       DISPLAY WS-NUMBER(WS-I)
    END-PERFORM.

    STOP RUN.
